{"serial": "85017", "department_serial": 69, "code": "BM3029", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "A statistical foundation of machine learning", "ch": "統計機器學習基礎"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lin, Chen"], "ch": ["林澂"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "R3", "room": "112"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "生醫科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Biomedical Sciences and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 40, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程探討機器學習的統計本質，探索了機器學習如何通過統計估計來概括資料模式，最終利用構建模型，並可利用這些模型進行類似條件下收集的資料進行分類，課程從基本的統計概念開始，包括概率論、統計估計技術以及關鍵的統計分佈。課程接著深入研究各種回歸模型，如線性回歸、多元回歸和邏輯回歸，以及一系列分類器。課程的一個關鍵組成部分是對特徵提取技術和降維方法的深入探討，包括主成分分析（PCA）和線性判別分析（LDA）。在全面概述當代深度學習範式的同時，課程還深入討論了規範化標準。通過理論知識與實踐應用的結合，本課程旨在賦予學生促進對統計基礎如何支撐機器學習不斷發展, 並將這些概念和方法未來可用於相關領域中。", "en": "Statistics is a fundamental aspect of machine learning. This course delves into how machine learning strives to create models capable of describing data through statistical estimation. These models effectively categorize data collected under similar conditions. We begin with the basic statistical concepts, including probability theory, statistical estimation, and common statistical distributions. The course then introduces various regression models such as linear regression, multiple regression, logistic regression, and an array of classifiers. Additionally, it covers the fundamentals of feature extraction and methods for dimension reduction, including principal component analysis and linear discriminant analysis. An overview of modern deep learning and regularization norms is also discussed. By integrating the fundamental concepts, the course aims to equip students with the ability to understand the recent development of machine learning and apply the learned skills to real-world challenges they may encounter."}, "outline": {"ch": "第1-2周\n機器學習相關機率論\n 隨機試驗與樣本空間\n 事件機率及隨機變數\n 離散及連續數值機率分布及函式\n第3-4周\n機器學習常用到的統計機率模型\n 伯努利分布 (Bernoulli Distribution)\n 二項分布 (Binomial Distribution)\n 均勻分布 (Uniform Distribution)\n 常態分布 (Normal Distribution)\n第5-6周\n機器學習常用統計\n 母體與樣本估計\n 信賴區間\n 假設檢定\n第7-8周\n迴歸分析\n 迴歸常用的損失函數\n 線性迴歸及多重線性迴歸\n第9周 期中考\n第10-11周\n羅吉式迴歸\n Sigmoid 函數\n 最大概似估計\n 羅吉斯迴歸求參數的方法\n第11-13周\n常見分類器介紹\n 分類常用的損失函數\n 貝式分類器\n 線性分類器\n 決策樹\n 向量支持機器\n第14-15周\n統計降維法\n 線性區別分析\n 主成分分析\n第16-17周\n深度學習概述\n 特徵提取及梯度下降法\n 正規化參數\n 模型評估\n第18周 期末考", "en": "Week 1-2\nProbability theories for machine learning\n Randomize trials and sample space\n Probability of events and random variables\n Discrete and continuous probability distributions and functions\nWeek 3-4\nCommon distributions for machine learning\n Bernoulli Distribution\n Binomial Distribution\n Uniform Distribution\n Normal Distribution\nWeek 5-6\nStatistics estimations for machine learning\n Population parameter and sample estimate\n Confident interval\n Hypothesis testing\nWeek 7-8\nLinear regression\n Commonly used loss functions for regression\n Linear and multiple linear regression\nWeek 9 Mid-term Exam\nWeek 10-11\nLogistic regression\n Sigmoid function\n Maximal likelihood function\n Estimate a logistic regression\nWeek 11-13\nIntroduction on commonly used classifiers\n Loss functions for classifiers\n Naive bayes classifier\n Linear discriminant\n Decision Tree\n Support Vector Machine\nWeek 14-15\nDimension Reduction\n Linear discriminant analysis\n Principal component analysis\nWeek 16-17\nOverview on Deep learning\n Feature extractions and gradient decent algorithm\n Parameter Regularization\n Model validation\nWeek 18 Final Exam"}, "textbook": {"ch": "自編教材", "en": "Handouts"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中30％、期末40％、出席10％、作業20％", "en": "Midterm exam 30％、Final exam 40％、Attendance rate: 10％、Homework 20％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "預約", "en": "By Appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "計算分析領域\n\n\n、\n\n\n醫學電子資訊與影像處理\n\n\n、\n\n\n轉譯醫學\n\n\n、\n\n\n計算神經科學", "en": "計算分析領域\n\n\n、\n\n\n醫學電子資訊與影像處理\n\n\n、\n\n\n轉譯醫學\n\n\n、\n\n\n計算神經科學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "學習數物化、醫學、生物等科學基礎與精進知識、思辨邏輯及運用能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "執行實驗設計、數據分析與推論的能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉臨床醫學，並培養生醫器材或材料之設計、開發、及場域應用的能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉感測元件原理、訓練製造、設計與整合智慧系統", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "發掘、探究、解析、處理以及重構問題", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "培養多層面跨域整合與團隊合作", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "瞭解專業知識與人本倫理間的調和、以及技術對環境、社會之影響，並能持續學習", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["自我評量/同儕互評"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Learn the basics of mathematics, physics, chemistry, medicine, biology and their applications in healthcare", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Ability to perform experimental design, data analysis and inference", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Familiar with clinical medicine, and cultivate the ability of design, development, and field applications of biomedical devices or materials", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Familiar with the principles of sensing elements, learn the ability to design, manufacture and integrate intelligent systems", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "The ability to discover, 